reviewText: Mark may never win an Oscar, but he will always get the best movie hunk award! If there were such a thing. These are 3 of his best, not including The Italian Job.
I love the triple play sets. Sometimes I will find them that seem tailored for me specifically. This is one of those.
Two 5 star movies, one 4 star movie, cant beat this collection! Mark is the man!
DVD did not work.  We have a Blu Ray Player and it wouldn't work.  Sent it back for a refund.  Love two of these movies though!  The Fighter and Shooter are great!

3 great movies for 1 low price!!! Can't beat the action of The Shooter. The Fighter is an intense drama. Four Brothers is a great action/ drama. I recommend this Triple Feature set to Mark Wahlberg fans and action/ drama fans!! Blu-ray quality is top-notch!!!
Great set of movies. Delivered on time.

I love this package of 3.  I am an action fan and was not disappointed.  I would suggest these to any movie buff who loves action and
a good story.  The price was definitely right.
Good Movies had to clean to watch
It's Mark Wahlberg, what more do you need to know?
